Dancing Blade - JAP - DC
RELEASE DATE : 12/12/2000       PLATFORM : DC/DreamCast
ORIGIN : JAP           FILE FORMAT : .CDi/DiscJuggler
CD'S/RAR'S : cd1 001-026         TYPE  : Interactive Anime
                      cd2 001-027
Dancing Blade is an enhanced port of the Playstation
voice novel of the same name. Dreamcast version boasts
24 frames per sec animation, it is an anime which lets
you determine the outcome based on how you answer various
questions that arise as the story unfolds. It is basically like
a voice animated version of a Choose Your Adventure book.
